n\n\n\n<p>Whether your home is traditional or minimalistic or modern, metal adds a subtle sheen to the interiors with its presence around you. That\u2019s why we recommend a metal sofa cum bed design. Choose a wrought iron base for this design and let it create a sturdy sofa and bed for you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181156\/metal-sofa-cum-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"A metal sofa cum bed design with a sturdy frame adds a subtle sheen to the interiors\" class=\"wp-image-34103\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181156\/metal-sofa-cum-bed-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181156\/metal-sofa-cum-bed-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181156\/metal-sofa-cum-bed-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181156\/metal-sofa-cum-bed-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Metal sofa cum bed design with a sturdy frame<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sofa Cum Double Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Feel like a royal with this kind of sofa cum bed. It is plush, expansive and touches all the right notes of a sofa and a king or queen bed. Throw in some luxe cushions, throws, and there you go, your modern double bed sofa is all set to take you in its comfy embrace. Sleep and sit well while you are on it!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08181151\/sofa-cum-double-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"A sofa cum double bed design touches all the right notes of a sofa and a king or queen bed\" class=\"wp-image-34106\" srcset=\"htt